  <brief_title>Intrathecal Mg in Gynecologic Laparoscopic Surgeries.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Addition of Magnesium Sulfate in Spinal Anesthesia on Surgeon Satisfaction and Postoperative Pain in Gynecologic Laparoscopic Surgeries.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Assiut University</agency>
